This paper discusses the automation of e-journal preservation systems, which involves the ingestion and management of large amounts of digital content. This topic is closely related to several sub-categories in computer science, including digital libraries (cs.DL), information retrieval (cs.IR), cryptography and security (cs.CR), machine learning (cs.LG), and computer networks (cs.CY).
